channelMetadataRenderer.title: Muse Asia
channelMetadataRenderer.description:
Set up in 1992, Muse Communication Co., Ltd. is an all-comprehensive animation company dealing with the production and distribution of Japan’s latest animation. The company also has marketing expertise and years of experience in the development of official merchandise. With a multi-dimensional team, the company is at the forefront of the animation industry across Asia.

The company is also actively developing diverse ways to bring our content and products to enthusiasts. We have distribution points in places like Shanghai and Singapore, and are working to bring all-encompassing services and experiences to fans in Asia.

Based in Sunny Singapore, Muse Communication Singapore is an active branch company of MUSE Communication Co., Ltd. We are a young team armed with fresh ideas and perspectives on the animation industry. We bring to you Muse Asia, a YouTube channel focused on anime and ACG-related content.

Subscribe and follow us now for exciting new events and video content!
